com.jack.dicewars.dice_wars.game

Class NullPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jack.dicewars.dice_wars.game.Player
      • com.jack.dicewars.dice_wars.game.NullPlayer

  • public class NullPlayer
extends Player
    Acts as the owner to a colorless Territory. Will always lose battles, have the colorless territory color, and never has an active turn.
